Day11 - ATS Resume Optimizer & Resume Generator

📌 Project Overview

This project focuses on optimizing an existing resume for maximum ATS (Applicant Tracking System) compatibility and recruiter relevance using AI. The resume is tailored according to a target job description while maintaining 100% factual accuracy.

🎯 Objective

- Analyze an existing resume.
- Compare it with a target Job Description.
- Identify missing keywords and skills.
- Generate an ATS-friendly resume.
- Improve recruiter visibility and job application success.

📂 Inputs

1. Existing Resume
2. Target Job Description

⚙️ Tools Used

- Claude AI
- LinkedIn
- Naukri
- Indeed
- Company Career Pages
- Microsoft Word
- Google Docs
- FlowCV
- Overleaf
- Canva

🚀 Process

1. Upload the existing resume.
2. Obtain a target Job Description.
3. Use the ATS Resume Optimizer prompt.
4. Generate ATS Match Score.
5. Perform Gap Analysis.
6. Identify missing keywords and skills.
7. Generate an optimized ATS-friendly resume.
8. Save the final resume.
9. Capture screenshots of the analysis and output.

📊 Outputs

ATS Match Score

- Overall Match Score
